Class Biome

  • java.lang.Object
    • ue7.Biome
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Village>

    public class Biome
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Village>
    This class provides a "Biome", which can store multiple numbers of Villages. It has to have a name and a kind of biome (e.g. "desert", "gras"...).
    Author:
    Paul Jureschek, Michael Kinzkofer
